{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"barInfo":{"barName":"骁","description":"开放自由的类贴吧式留言板","isMainBar":true,"isPublic":true},"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>上午去的，呆了四十分钟左右。</p> ","floor":1,"pid":0,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:27:16","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","sourceUrl":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>这是外观，和楚河汉街一样的民国风，分三层。说是目前最大的小米之家。</p><br><p><img src=\"/xbar/ce4306e9814cfa91a8.jpg\"></p> ","floor":2,"pid":8504,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:28:17","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>虽然有三层，但每一层的面积也不算很大。不过摆的东西是真的多，比普通的小米之家多了不少。给人很强烈的紧凑感。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/f7a8e70f59a98d7934.jpg\"></p> ","floor":3,"pid":8505,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:32:10","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>投影仪、路由器、扫地机器人、台灯、小爱同学被摆放在一起，足可见空间的紧凑。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/0c8a2fcfd15613052d.jpg\"></p> ","floor":4,"pid":8506,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:33:50","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>二楼是米家有品的专区，有很多平时不常看见的隶属于米家App里的产品。比如云米的智能冰箱、不知道哪个合作伙伴的锅碗瓢盆，以及玩具等……有孩子坐在地毯上玩玩具。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/5a3c826ca2365689f3.jpg\"><img src=\"/xbar/789171efc4c659ba80.jpg\"></p><p>二楼也是有们的，有面向对面大街的门。</p> ","floor":5,"pid":8507,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:37:59","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>三楼像是家居馆，似乎想营造一个使用米家全套设备的家庭的场景。但显然还没有营造好，仍然显乱和紧凑。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/23589ab3181e781fca.jpg\"></p> ","floor":6,"pid":8508,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:39:23","replyCount":1,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897,"initComments":{"list":[{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"三楼不仅有沙发，还有床来着。 ","createTime":"2018-10-02 18:39:59","id":2760,"replyId":0,"replyUserCode":"","authorInfo":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}],"pageInfo":{"total":1,"pageSize":10,"current":1},"total":1,"totalPages":1}},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>从楼梯上看一楼，是这样的场景。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/fae7aa34d021c9f9b3.jpg\"></p> ","floor":7,"pid":8509,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:40:46","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>小米在附近打了不少广告，还包下了街头剧场举办什么活动。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/c4c3a0b6f04b5d2e54.jpg\"></p><br><p><img src=\"/xbar/beba3016e276fad5ed.jpg\"></p><br><p><img src=\"/xbar/4ef248a4e5b21d1f59.jpg\"></p> ","floor":8,"pid":8510,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:42:19","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>舞台上有孩子在欺负米兔。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/8fa4790672d529323b.jpg\"></p> ","floor":9,"pid":8511,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:43:09","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897},{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","content":"<p>顺便去附近的万达广场看了看原来的小米之家，明显清净不少。另外新开的旗舰店目前连个像样的前台都没有。。然后路过苹果店，看到了iPhone XS和iPhone XS Max。</p><p><img src=\"/xbar/a52c9948f03b17e387.jpg\"></p> ","floor":10,"pid":8512,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:45:02","replyCount":0,"signKey":"","source":"","tid":2897}],"pageInfo":{"total":10,"pageSize":30,"current":1},"threadInfo":{"author":"孙天骁","authorCode":"admin","classifyName":"闲谈","goodClassifyName":"","id":2897,"isGood":true,"isPicture":true,"isRepost":false,"postTime":"2018-10-02 18:27:16","replyCount":10,"title":"今天去参观了新开业的武汉小米之家楚河汉街旗舰店。","topState":0},"tid":2897,"total":10,"totalPages":1,"viewHost":false,"users":{"admin":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","r